       Frontend - E commerce

1. Create angular project - ng new cart
2. Run angular - ng s -o
3. Add bootstrap, font awesome, google fonts
4. Lazy loading - Its a process of loading components and modules
                - It improves application load time speed

                ng g m products --route products --module app.module

5. Create a components should lazy loaded in the products module
      -> all-products - ng g c products/all-products
      -> cart - ng g c products/cart
      -> wish list - ng g c products/wish-list

6. Designing of the components
7. Create angular services for API calling
      -> ng g s products/api
8. Import httpClientModule in products module
9. Integration
10. Designing of wish list and cart
11. Search for products
    ng g p produts/pipes/filter
